=== Series 3 (2018) === This series takes a more topical tone with Ullman's impersonations of world leaders taking center stage. No longer is the show set in Great Britain but on the global stage. Sketches produced for the reformatted show ''[[Tracey Breaks the News]]'' are utilised for this series.
