'''Sveta Klara''' is a settlement in the southern part of [[Zagreb, Croatia]]. Once a separate village, it is now administered as a neighbourhood of the city district of [[Novi Zagreb – zapad]]. The population is 9,560 (as of Census 2011).<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.zagreb.hr/default.aspx?id=15058 | language = Croatian | title = Gradska četvrt Novi Zagreb - zapad Mjesni odbori 15. Mjesni odbor Sveta Klara | publisher = [[City of Zagreb]] | accessdate = 2016-07-07}}</ref>

